# BillableEmployeesList(title, employees)
-```
{
    "type": "AdaptiveCard",
    "body": [
        ${join(where(createArray(Title(title), Header(), EmployeeRows(employees)), item => item != ''), ',')}
    ],
    "$schema": "http://adaptivecards.io/schemas/adaptive-card.json",
    "version": "1.2"
}
```

# Title(title)
- IF: ${ dialog.foreach.pageindex == 1 }
    - ```
    {
        "type": "TextBlock",
        "size": "Large",
        "text": "${title}",
        "fontType": "Default"
    }
    ```
- ELSE:
    - ``````

